# Changelog

All notable changes to **DateTimeBuddy** will be documented in this file.

## [2.0.5] - 2025-07-27

### Added
- `compare(other: Date | DateTimeBuddy)` — Returns `-1`, `0`, or `1` when comparing two instances.
- `equalsDateOnly(other: Date | DateTimeBuddy)` — Compares only year, month, and day, ignoring time.
- `diffIn(other: Date | DateTimeBuddy, unit?: 'seconds' | 'minutes' | 'hours' | 'days')` — Returns signed difference in specified unit.
- `toUTCString()` — Returns standard UTC string representation of the date.
- `toJSON()` — Alias to `toISOString()`, returns JSON-compatible ISO string.
- `toLocaleString(locale?: string)` — Returns locale-aware date and time string.
- `toLocaleDateString(locale?: string)` — Returns locale-aware date-only string.
- Extended tests and examples showcasing new methods.

### Changed
- Updated documentation and README with new methods.
- Test script output now includes detailed comparison, diffIn, and localized formatting examples.

### Fixed
- No bugs found.

---